In german school. we are writting a "news paper" and everyone else has to write stories and stuff.. so this is one i came up with, its about my favorite song..

Redundant.

because i love this song. 

The definition of Redundant: Characterized by or containing an excess or superfluous amount. 

This song,was written by Billie Joe Armstrong, the lead singer of green day. It is about loving someone so much that love can't express how much you DO love them.

We're living in repetition.
Content in the same old shtick again.
Now the routine's turning to contention,
Like a production line going over and over and over, roller coaster

Now I cannot speak, I lost my voice
I'm speechless and redundant
'Cause I love you's not enough
I'm lost for words.

Choreographed and lack of passion
Prototypes of what we were
Went full circle 'til I'm nauseous
Taken for granted now
I waste it, faked it, ate it, now i hate it

Cos I cannot speak, I lost my voice
I'm speechless and redundant
'Cause I love you's not enough
I'm lost for words.

Now I cannot speak, I lost my voice
I'm speechless and redundant
'Cause I love you's not enough
I'm lost for words.

Now I cannot speak, I lost my voice
I'm speechless and redundant
'Cause I love you's not enough
I'm lost for words.

mhm
on myspace to, but nobody else is on. 
but thats alright 

Ive been listening to some of Green Day's old stuff for the past couple of days, dont get me wrong, i still love them. Ive been just listening to Corey's CDs that he let me borrow, so i really havent had that much time to go back and listen to some green day. (-: i re-fell in love with Worry Rock, Take Back, Suffocate, FOD, Basket Case, Do Da Da, Ha Ha Your Dead,Best Thing in Town, WORDS I MIGHT HAVE ATE, Tightwad hill,panic song, and All the time. 

Report Cards came out, not toooooooo happy about them.

So its been forever since i wrote in here
life has been very good.

Recently::
I'm still falling for my Boyfriend, Corey ♥
no more braces!!!!!!!!
got a new cell.. pretty kool thing has a camera and AIM. Same number tho
Midterms are soon
Youth Group

Wow, this break was AMAZING!

Friday~ Parties in everyclass at school! Oh yeah. Finished up Cinderlla man in American Studies, it was probably the sadddest movie. Well not really, but it was pretty sad. I also found out something pretty rad!...you all will have to wait til Wednsday tho

Also, went to see King Kong with Corey on friday. It was a little long. But an overall good movie

Saturday- Christmas Eve. Got ready for church, went to church, did churchly things with Timmy , Derek, Timmy's sister and my sisters. Then went out to dinner at Steak and Ale with my Aunt. Then my mom drove me and laur back to church for the Candlelight Service so we can play in the bell choir with Bri and Nat. Because we are that kool.

Sunday-  Christmas, very good! Got alot of GreenDay things, like books, Cd's, mag's. But most of all I got my iPod nano. Its very kool. its black  Corey came over so we cpuld exchanged gifts. I love the necklace he got me. Once he left, i still had to get my self ready. Then we headed over to my Oma's [grandmoms in german]

Monday- Resting Day from Christmas, got used to iTunes.

Tuesday- Christmas at My Aunt and Uncles. Hung out with my 5 year old cuzz. Hes awesome. We played with hotwheels (oh yeah) and some action figures. I also agreed to come over and babysit him the next day.

Weds- Babysitting my cuz, then went out to the movies with Corey. We were going to see a 9:40 Producers...but when we went into the theater it was full with no seats.. so that kinda stunk. So we went with his mom and sister to see Family Stone. Pretty funny move and half sad.

Thursday- Christmas with my dad's side. Kool time. They were over and we all just chilled out. Played King Kong on the PS2 and DDR.

Friday- Chilled out agian.

Saturday- New Years Eve. Made plans for New Years.  Went to Seth's party for a while. Christine couldnt go, so i eneded up being the only girl there... Watched the guys play pool, and DDR. Later, me and corey came back to my house to celebrate new years with my family. The girls wanted to see Corey play me in DDR, which they did. And he beat me most of the time  

Today- My Aunt and Uncle and my cuz'z r coming over for Lunch. And later I have no clue..

Christmas is almost here! It the eve of christmas eve, and yet we have school.. so im kinda bummed out about that. I love chirstmas, its pretty much amazing. This christmas is going to be 'specally awesome with Francis and Rosa coming up from Arizonia/Nevada area.  I really cant wait to see them! I miss my older cuzz soo much.

Recently, I have cut my hair and had it highlighted for Winter Formal. The hair cut is way to shot, due to a couple mistakes that the hair lady made. Winter formal was a great time [ and four months for me and corey], and i am still shocked that Corey came back to be with me just for a dance. It still brightens my day. i finally go to meet Jenna's Corey also. 

My mom put together a Church Christmas Celebration, which was so much fun. She did a good job running the whole thing. She also directed a play which i was in

Mr.Strange- Dad
Mrs. S- Mom
Me- Janelle
Timmy- Steve
Brian- Mikey
Kristin- Tiffany

Basically it was a play about a family who got side tracked with the tru meaning of christmas.
"What if i was chineese!!!" -- timmy before the play.. hes one funny kid.

I am also involved in the churches bell Choir with laur, Natalie, and Brian. I play bells , C6, D6, and E6.. oh yeah

Hope everyone has a happy holiday

At Reedman and stuff. Thuey have an area with the internet.. but they blocked all the good sites and stuff. Mysapce and AIM are blocked .. xanga im not even gonna try to go onto.
Its nice here. pretty quiet i guess. We r in the chevy building at Reedman. Katy is here with me, shes on the other computer. 

We are just relaly waiting for my parents to wrap up the paper work for the new car. its nioce.

Weds- Went to school, corey<3 decided not to go.. chilled in Study hall... then lunch, the girls and i went to the lib found oksanna, the media room was closed b/c of a class room that was in there, so the 5 of us were on Oksanas computer.. went home, and then went over to Corey's for dinner and then we went to go see Rent with his family.. which was a great time!!!

Thrus- Thanksgiving!! Our heater broke. )-: so it was FREEZING! Later on my family and I went to my Aunts and Uncles for thanksgiving. Super time. Played Pinball and Monopoly (-: 

Fri- Heater still broken, and the guy finally came out to fix it. Sammy was going NUTS over him, barking and crying. Finally the guy left, and my dad took me to coreys. Coreys dad came for me and we went to the Bowling Alley where I met up with Corey. We did two games (one he won and one I won), then I met some of his extended family, went back to his house, sat around, played on the gutiar and Super Nintendo. Ate some dinner and then watched Hitch.

Sat- Went shopping at Williow Grove with Jillian W. Then later on was vikkis sweet 16. That was a blast! It was at a Russian Resturant in NE Philly. The people only spoke russian and the entertainers that sang only sang Russian. The other Entertainers were really good! they did magic, danced.. the usal. Me, Rosie, Oksana, Jill, Monica, and Briana all danced to Russian Techno/ American Techno.. fun fun (-: 

Sun- Went to church, then  went to do the crafts for the first advent. I got stamped by Brian lol! Came home, and made plans with Corey. Watched the game for a bit, then went to get Corey so we could go to the movies. On our way there we almost got hit by a drunk driver!! o-:  it was soooooooo scary. it was. Then we got Corey and went to the movies. The mall and theater was not that packed.. i was surprised.. but when we went into the Theater it was pretty full. 

Mon- went to coreys with the guys to play d&d with them

Tues- i was hyper

Friday-- Day of the show... Corey was acting all weird... but i guess it was b/c he was nervous... nice turnout  for the show... go to nifty 50's... hang out with ppl there... 

Saturday--Didnt go to german school... b/c of the 2 shows.. both had nice turn outs.  Then i was supposed to go out to dinner with corey but that never happend )-: ... i wanted to do something nice for him, so i went out and i bought him Balloons and a card and left it at his door.. lol (-: 

Sunday-- Went to church--> then youth group. We were making posters for an upcoming christmas babysitting at our church..brian being brian drew hott pink smiles on all of the posters and then drew on my moms hand.... later on went to Seths with corey to learn wat Corey does on his weekends lol...then went out to dinner with coreys family...

Monday-- Footloose dance practice, then cast party. Cast party was fun, me, britt, mariel, el, and mike moshing to Footloose, hanging out with corey, and listen to ppl make prank phone calls. 

Yesterday-- Felt sick, went out to the movies with my family and saw Chicken Little.

Sunday- went to church, saw natalie, timmy, derek, katie and kirsten. kool beans.
then i went to see flight plan with Corey<3...it was a good movie i liked it a bunch.

Monday- Went to school.. it was cold. 

Tuesday- Sprianed my finger in gym class attempting to catch a football ( which i did..) Corey wasnt feeling good, so he went home. Homecoming assembly. Buss ride home was soo freeking amazing... listend to Anthony's Ipod, and i also got tickled and poked to death.. *fun* and Went to the doctors.
moms and dads 20th wedding ann... so i got to babysit also.

Today-- figner kills... and in study hall..

Friday- It was cold and rainy durning school..we had a boring asssembly and me and josh drew on brents pants with Calk... bus ride home= fun. Listened to Anthony's Ipod and talked to trisha. 

Later on  me and Corey<3 went to a halloween part @ David's house. It was fun! Played Air hockey with Eva, played Scene it? with everybody, danced to Frank Sinatra with Corey for like a half an hour even though it didnt seem like it, hung around , watched paul and john beat eachother up with swords and Pvc pips. 

Saturday-- german school/ oktoberfest. Danced to Festive German songs with Laura.

Later , katy, nikki and the rents are going to go down town to see a show and me and laura are going to be home and bored all night.

i was being a loser with a smile... and i was on a website and i found this and thought it was adorable, so i had to post it

when you can't stop smiling after you talk
to him and you still get butterflies in your 
stomach, & that huge smile across your face 
everytime you see him , that lets you know he 
will always mean something to you . <3
i remeber when i used to eat sardeens for dinner.... by rosie..

im really sleepy..and i have alot of homework to do and i really dont feel like going to the acting class..

and...2 months today..im very happy!

yeah so the party was fun, i got to hang with Julia!! omg she is getting soo big!! 7 years old! For anyone who doesnt know, she was adopted from china, she is adorable and my little buddy. And wow, Rachel (her sister, but not really...they were from 2 different families) is talking!! Before she NEVER talked! and now she does
I also got to meet my cus'z girlfriend--Misty..she seemes to be nice! Zoe of course was adorable,like she always is. The polish boys were fighting with Forks lol.

but, i did miss corey..alot, i wished that he was there. <3 i did get to talk to him for a while on the phone and that made me very happy :D

Friday- Drama ..fun.. then went home, cleaned up, then picked up laura from laurens, and picked up corey <3, went to blockbuster and rented movies, came home, ate pizza and watch Fever pitch with my family..then me and corey<3 went into the basement and that is our buisness. (: 

Saturday- PSAT testing whoo hoo. i was going to go to the game with corey<3 but then it was cancelled...

Went to stefs party, fun fun fun! it twas! 

Sunday- Church, nobody really there but Amanda, and Ashley, then came home and found out that Corey couldnt come to day, to Zoes party.. but its all alright <3

And yeah, made plans for the weekend. and its going to be an amazing weekend!!!!!!!!!!!!!! :)  <3333333333333333333333333333333333333

Random Myspace thing that I thought was cute:
Did u know? B4 u go to sleep at night there is 1 person of the opposite sex thinking of u. They want you they want to kiss u, They want to be with u they are always thinking about u b4 they go to sleep at night they are longing to be with u.

Monday- went to the acting class, which was alright, corey <3,vikki, paul and ellie were there. I read a poem that I wrote. and then i went home and talked to people online, and then Corey <3 on the phone.

Tuesday- Finished up all computer graphics stuff

Yesterday- Progress reports; i did okay, i just need to work on American Studies and Bio.

Becca was supposed to vist..but the school kicked her out for not haveing a pass..

There was also drama yesterday, fun in a bun as steffie would say. Me and stef switched shoes, b/c we are kool. 

After drama, Corey <3 inivted me over to his house for dinner, b/c it was a Yom Kippor(sp?) dinner, with his family and other families. When we got to his house we watched T.V. (Sponge Bob..oh yeah! (: , Met his sister Mel, and hung around, then ate dinner which was REALLY good. Then got annyoed by the little kids and talked... but i have to say, i was really sad when my dad pulled up to get me..

Oh yeah! my new shoes came early! they are awesome... and pink!! :D

friday- decided not to go out anywere, just spend sometime with the family...corey left to go to pittsburg, and i was texting him alot. I was having a online poking war with short freshman anthony on the bus b/c we r just that cool and just that BORED.

Saturday- No german school, Jillian's party/shopping spree at williow grove. Me, Katie, Jenna, Jillian, Beta, and Oksana were all there shopping was fun. i bought my self a shirt from american eagle with a smile face on it, and a green kinda sorta obnoxious track jaket that says "beautiful" (even though im not) and we walked around, then jills mom came and drove us back to jillians. when we got back to her house Kimmy was there!! I HAVENT SEEN HER IN FOREVER! and we chilled, she opened up her gifts, we watched "A walk to remember"...lol.. me and stef were craking up during that movie!! I <3 Her.  then we ate dinner and played with her doggie and the gutair.

when i came home i updated the xanga and then got a new layout for it b/c the one i had on there was getting old. 

Sunday- We didnt go to church,sorry natalie if you r reading this. My mom wasnt up to it. Me and My mom odered me a new pair of chuck's .. they are Neon Pink and they are awesome

So yeah my 2 days off were awesome

Tuesday-- we were driving to Ocean City NJ..we stayed @ the Porta Call hotel. Hung out by the pool, went in the ocean and walked on the boardwalk. I bought a couple nice things on thier also.

Wednsday-- went for a walk by the ocean @ 7:30... then hung around the board walk, then drove around the board walk looking for the pop corn place b/c the one on 14th street was closed... then we drove home

When I got home i unpacked and then I got invited over to Corey's <3

so im leaving today....who knows were i am going... my parents r keeping it a surprise... 

yesterday i went to corey's after German Club(oh yeah Jeanne, Anthony, gabi and Christine!) and Jump-Roping in the weight room.. i had a good time, and i hope he did to. We watched Wimbolton... or how ever you spell it, ate dinner and played Scrabble with his mom and dad.

Friday:: Went home after school...hung around the house then went out with my family to get ny dad something, I got him 2 Led Zep CD's "Early Days & Latter Days". 

Later on went to the LM and ANC game with Corey<3 and paul which was awesome..even though we lost..but it was still alotta fun. I got to see alots of people like... Ashley M, Sam, Sam, John, Anthony from the bus, Lauren, Jamie, Katie, Thanu, Vikki, Vikki, Jess, Shannon...and more people who i dont feel like typing.

Saturday:: Dads b-day!! Went to german schoool.. )': but my mom picked me and my sisters up early (: ! My dad opened up his gifts ...then we headed out to Walmart where i bought by self "warning" CD by Greenday--which makes it only ONE MORE cd i need by them! i made plans with corey to go to the movies. Then we went out to dinner to Red Robin, which was awesome! 

After dinner my parents drove me to Coreys<3 house, we decided to go on a double date with seth and christine to see just like heaven-  After coreys family ate, me and him sat in thier little den-ish type thing where he played me a song by Dispatch... and it was Amazing..even though he thinks it wasnt..it was!!

Then we headed out to the movies,  seth and christine found us...the movie was good, but seth and christine fell alseep lol, they wouldnt wake up so corey txted them "wake up". Afterwords we headed back to coreys house to hang out somemore..... but I was sad that i had to leave, i didnt want to..
